main event: Two bright objects were observed crossing the sky from east to west at high speed in Long Beach, California.
interesting points: The objects appeared to be maneuvering in the air., The sighting lasted for 20 minutes., No known aircraft were operating in the area at the time of the sighting., The conclusion stated that the objects could not be definitively identified as aircraft or balloons due to insufficient data., The report was part of the historical Project Blue Book investigation.
